room_title: Escape room "Jackpot" by The Gamers Escape Room in Temecula
review: I absolutely love this escape room ! I have been to many and their new room is awesome! The owners are super friendly and my friends all had a great time !

room_title: Escape room "Jackpot" by The Gamers Escape Room in Temecula
review: We had a team bonding experience a few months back when they had opened. The staff was family friendly. The room we had done was interactive with plenty to keep us all busy. I enjoyed the theme. We have done a lot of rooms, so this room was more basic for us. Not bad to play. Overall a fun for beginners.
